---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
const title = "Terms of Service | NiO Pictures — Katy TX";
const description = "Terms of Service for NiO Pictures. Photography service terms, website usage, intellectual property, and limitation of liability.";
const canonical = "https://niopictures.com/terms.html";
const ogImage = "https://niopictures.com/assets/images/og-home.webp";
const extraHead = "";
---

<BaseLayout title={title} description={description} canonical={canonical} ogImage={ogImage} noIndex={true}>
  <Fragment slot="head" set:html={extraHead} />
<a href="#main-content" class="skip-link" style="position:absolute;top:-40px;left:1rem;background:var(--gold);color:var(--black);padding:0.5rem 1rem;border-radius:2px;font-family:var(--font-accent);font-size:0.7rem;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;z-index:9999;transition:top var(--dur-fast);" onfocus="this.style.top='1rem'" onblur="this.style.top='-40px'">Skip to main content</a>

  <nav class="nav" role="navigation" aria-label="Main navigation">
    <a href="/" class="nav-logo">Ni<span>O</span> Pictures</a>
    <div class="nav-links">
      <a href="/event-photography-katy-tx.html">Events</a>
      <a href="/family-photography-katy-tx.html">Family</a>
      <a href="/blog.html">Blog</a>
      <a href="/portfolio.html">Portfolio</a>
      <a href="/about.html">About</a>
      <a href="/contact.html">Contact</a>
    </div>
    <a href="https://niopictures.pixieset.com/booking/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-primary nav-cta">Book Now</a>
    <button class="nav-toggle" aria-label="Open menu" aria-expanded="false"><span></span><span></span><span></span></button>
  </nav>

  <div class="nav-mobile" role="dialog" aria-label="Mobile navigation">
    <a href="/event-photography-katy-tx.html">Events</a>
    <a href="/family-photography-katy-tx.html">Family</a>
    <a href="/blog.html">Blog</a>
    <a href="/portfolio.html">Portfolio</a>
    <a href="/about.html">About</a>
    <a href="/contact.html">Contact</a>
    <a href="https://niopictures.pixieset.com/booking/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="nav-mobile-cta">Book a Session →</a>
  </div>

  <main id="main-content">

  <div style="padding: calc(var(--section-pad) + 4rem) 0 3rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-light);">
    <div class="container" style="max-width: 760px;">
      <p class="eyebrow" style="margin-bottom:1rem;">Legal</p>
      <div class="gold-line"></div>
      <h1 class="display-xl" style="margin-bottom:0.75rem;">Terms of Service</h1>
      <p class="body-lg">By using this website or engaging NiO Pictures for photography services, you agree to the following terms.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="legal-body">
    <span class="effective-date">Effective date: March 1, 2026 &nbsp;·&nbsp; NiO Pictures, Katy, Texas</span>

    <h2 class="display-md">1. About NiO Pictures</h2>
    <p>NiO Pictures is a photography business operated by Palanivel, based in Katy, Texas. We provide event photography and family portrait services to clients in the greater Houston area including Katy, Sugar Land, Cypress, and Richmond, TX.</p>
    <p>Contact: <a href="mailto:niopictureskaty@gmail.com">niopictureskaty@gmail.com</a> &nbsp;·&nbsp; <a href="tel:2814093585">281-409-3585</a></p>

    <div class="legal-divider"></div>

    <h2 class="display-md">2. Website Use</h2>
    <p>By accessing niopictures.com, you agree to use this website lawfully and in accordance with these terms. You may not:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Scrape, copy, or reproduce content from this site without permission</li>
      <li>Use this site to distribute spam or malicious content</li>
      <li>Attempt to gain unauthorized access to any part of the website</li>
      <li>Use any automated tools to access or index the site without permission</li>
    </ul>

    <div class="legal-divider"></div>

    <h2 class="display-md">3. Photography Services</h2>

    <h3 class="display-sm">Booking & Deposits</h3>
    <p>Sessions are confirmed once a booking form is submitted and a date is agreed upon. Specific payment and deposit terms are communicated at the time of booking. NiO Pictures reserves the right to decline any booking at its discretion.</p>

    <h3 class="display-sm">Session Delivery</h3>
    <p>Edited images are delivered via a private online gallery (Pixieset) within the timeframe agreed upon at booking — typically 7–10 business days depending on the package selected. Delivery timelines may vary during peak seasons.</p>

    <h3 class="display-sm">Cancellations & Rescheduling</h3>
    <p>Cancellation and rescheduling policies are communicated at the time of booking. NiO Pictures reserves the right to reschedule sessions due to severe weather or circumstances outside our control.</p>

    <h3 class="display-sm">Additional Images</h3>
    <p>Each package includes a set number of edited images. Additional images beyond the package allowance are available at $20 per image, purchased through your private gallery.</p>

    <h3 class="display-sm">Prints & Products</h3>
    <p>Prints, wall art, and keepsake albums are ordered through your private Pixieset gallery. Product quality, pricing, and fulfillment are subject to Pixieset's terms and conditions.</p>

    <div class="legal-divider"></div>

    <h2 class="display-md">4. Intellectual Property</h2>
    <p>All photographs taken by NiO Pictures remain the intellectual property and copyright of Palanivel / NiO Pictures. All rights reserved.</p>
    <p>Upon delivery, clients receive a <strong style="color:var(--cream);">personal use license</strong> to print and share their images for non-commercial purposes. This includes sharing on personal social media, sending to family, and ordering prints for personal use.</p>
    <p>You may not:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Sell or license photographs taken by NiO Pictures to third parties</li>
      <li>Use images for commercial advertising or promotional purposes without prior written consent</li>
      <li>Claim ownership or authorship of photographs taken by NiO Pictures</li>
      <li>Apply filters or edits that significantly alter the images and present them as original NiO Pictures work</li>
    </ul>
    <p>NiO Pictures may use photographs from sessions for portfolio, website, and social media purposes, unless a written opt-out is requested at the time of booking.</p>

    <h3 class="display-sm">Website Content</h3>
    <p>All content on niopictures.com — including text, design, graphics, and code — is the property of NiO Pictures. You may not reproduce, republish, or distribute any content without written permission.</p>

    <div class="legal-divider"></div>

    <h2 class="display-md">5. Limitation of Liability</h2>
    <p>NiO Pictures makes every reasonable effort to deliver high-quality photography services. However, to the fullest extent permitted by applicable law:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>NiO Pictures is not liable for any indirect, incidental, or consequential damages arising from use of this website or photography services</li>
      <li>Our total liability for any claim arising from our services is limited to the amount paid for the specific session in question</li>
      <li>NiO Pictures is not responsible for technical issues with third-party platforms (Pixieset, Formspree, Google) that affect delivery</li>
    </ul>
    <p>Nothing in these terms limits liability for fraud, personal injury caused by negligence, or any other liability that cannot be excluded under Texas law.</p>

    <div class="legal-divider"></div>

    <h2 class="display-md">6. Third-Party Links</h2>
    <p>This website contains links to third-party websites including Pixieset, Google, Instagram, and Facebook. NiO Pictures is not responsible for the content, privacy practices, or terms of these external sites.</p>

    <div class="legal-divider"></div>

    <h2 class="display-md">7. Governing Law</h2>
    <p>These terms are governed by the laws of the State of Texas, United States. Any disputes arising under these terms shall be subject to the jurisdiction of the courts of Fort Bend County or Harris County, Texas.</p>

    <div class="legal-divider"></div>

    <h2 class="display-md">8. Changes to These Terms</h2>
    <p>NiO Pictures may update these Terms of Service at any time. Updated terms will be posted on this page with a new effective date. Continued use of the website after changes constitutes acceptance.</p>

    <div class="legal-divider"></div>

    <h2 class="display-md">9. Contact</h2>
    <p>Questions about these terms? Get in touch:</p>
    <p>
      <strong style="color:var(--cream);">NiO Pictures</strong><br>
      Katy, Texas, USA<br>
      <a href="mailto:niopictureskaty@gmail.com">niopictureskaty@gmail.com</a><br>
      <a href="tel:2814093585">281-409-3585</a>
    </p>

    <div style="margin-top:3rem; padding:1.5rem; background:var(--surface); border:1px solid var(--border-light); border-radius:2px;">
      <p style="margin:0; font-size:0.85rem; color:var(--muted);">See also: <a href="/privacy.html">Privacy Policy</a> &nbsp;·&nbsp; <a href="/contact.html">Contact Us</a> &nbsp;·&nbsp; <a href="/">Back to Home</a></p>
    </div>
  </div>

  </main>

  
</BaseLayout>
